room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Office" by Escape Artist in Charlotte
review: We had a great time! Conquered the Divinci Office Room, with a little help from Vinnie. I'll definitely be going back!!! Thanks for a great time!

room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Office" by Escape Artist in Charlotte
review: I've been here twice. I've done the Da Vinci Code and Area 51 and loved it. Great experience, great staff, and the rooms really get you thinking.

room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Office" by Escape Artist in Charlotte
review: We escaped DaVinci's office tonight! We had a great time. Vinny was awesome and helped us as we needed it. I can't wait to try the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Office" by Escape Artist in Charlotte
review: My husband and I had a great time! Since it wasn't busy we were able to take on Davinci's office by ourselves. The staff gave us help in getting through the room but overall a wonderful experience. Would recommend this place to anyone looking to spend an hour having fun while using your brain.
